Package com.TeamNumberOne.canbusbackend.Controller

Class ProjectManager

java.lang.Object
com.TeamNumberOne.canbusbackend.Controller.ProjectManager
@CrossOrigin @Controller @RequestMapping(path="/projects") public class ProjectManager extends Object
Creates a controller for the Project model, this allows the population of data in the model, and allows the model to be modified without full access to the model for the end user.
